data.description: Welcome to your cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom haven in the heart of Sturgeon. This home is perfect for empty nesters or those starting their homeownership journey. Your privacy is assured with a 6-foot wood fence, and there's a convenient 1-car garage. Inside, you'll find some window treatments, a 200-amp electrical panel, and energy-efficient vinyl windows. A newer front storm door adds style and security, while the concrete driveway makes parking a breeze. Nestled on a nice shaded corner lot, this property is a true gem. Don't miss your chance to call it home!
